gStreamer is a nice way to stream footage from the Raspi to a remote computer
using a local network. 

1) Follow instructions at link below to setup gStreamer

https://docs.emlid.com/navio2/common/dev/video-streaming/

2) If receive error message saying missing h.264

<sudo apt install gstreamer1.0-libav>

3) if receive error message saying missing h264parse

<sudo apt-get install gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad>

4) Look at first link for details on running.  

5) to disable autostart on Drone run following command. 

<sudo systemctl disable raspicam>
